  "schema:description": "This image depicts Martin Yan performing a cooking demonstration in the Cruess Hall Courtyard at UC Davis. During UC Davis\u2019 annual Picnic Day, Yan demonstrated chicken deboning and stir-frying in the Cruess Hall Courtyard. He invited alumnus Rawi Nanakul to assist with cooking and received a UC Davis apron and bottle of olive oil from a university representative.",
